<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">methodologies</ENAMEX>, and periodic <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">agency</ENAMEX> reporting on the status of
improvement efforts. At the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">agency</ENAMEX> or program level, it included
<ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">management</ENAMEX>'s public commitment to reduce fraud and errors, as
