<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">organizations</ENAMEX> to minimize losses and maximize opportunities. The
philosophy makes risk management a part of its organizational
culture and integrates risk <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">management</ENAMEX> into its day-to-day
practices and business activities. When this is achieved, risk
<ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">management</ENAMEX> becomes the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">business</ENAMEX> of everyone in the
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">organization</ENAMEX>.
